{"tid":1848081,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【行動】除左東鐵 大家唔會唔記得跨境巴士","createTime":"2020-01-28T09:53:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-28T10:00:35.000Z","uid":150386,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"ada74d66a04f44aefc03ff69cda90a3b0c984618","tid":1848081,"uid":150386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T09:53:49.000Z","msg":"東鐵固然要阻<br />\n但大家唔好唔記得跨境巴士<br />\n<br />\n當支那人坐唔到東鐵落嚟香港<br />\n自然會考慮跨境巴士<br />\n<br />\n所以要中斷兩地交通 <br />\n一定要搞跨境巴士<br />\n<br />\n行動成本極低 <br />\n兩三個人一team <br />\n用個噴漆就搞掂<br />\n<br />\n大家可以上網睇下跨境巴士站<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.eebus.com/#\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.eebus.com%2F%23&d=rcEdfnhTqGmqsB%2B6X%2FYCGQ8%2Bx5Wy5jX%2Bp0OgAvZs4CE%3D&h=ff9daf0c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.eebus.com/#</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">利申：唔鼓勵犯法行為，大家千奇唔好做</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"b88f4ead137ad7e8140c697b651e63148c0ff7fc","tid":1848081,"uid":150386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T09:54:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5867e6e29a966a0d851004b5eaaead980bb99048","tid":1848081,"uid":150386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T09:54:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fe4b94f0ef5072917f724e47b608f4a112da9e7b","tid":1848081,"uid":150386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T09:54:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cb4f38ec014308f0a4a3d74b3de21667ed985280","tid":1848081,"uid":150386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T09:54:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"363971bc1bba6ed8855fb80c112dedcf31cf944f","tid":1848081,"uid":9193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T09:55:22.000Z","msg":"現時主要的過境巴士總站如下：<br />\n<br />\n太子總站<br />\n旺角（鴉蘭街）總站<br />\n柯士甸道跨界巴士總站<br />\n圓方過境巴士總站<br />\n九龍塘（沙福道）公共運輸交匯處<br />\n荃灣（德海街）總站<br />\n落馬洲（新田）公共運輸交匯處<br />\n深圳灣口岸公共運輸交匯處<br />\n二號客運大樓旅遊車總站<br />\n港珠澳大橋香港口